DOC.LD:
   The average interest rate on 15-year mortgages, a popular option
for refinancing, dipped to 5.93% this week from 6% the week before,
and now is the lowest ever recorded.

DOC.TE:
   That means the Packers' season-ticket waiting list dropped by
about 800, a team spokesman told the Milwaukee Journal Sentinel;
57,500 names remain on the list.
